{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I found the actual issue with the browser artifacts: the chat lane is expanding the page height instead of using an internal transcript scroller, so the summary bubbles were far below the initial viewport. I\u2019m doing a final page-scroll c...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_149", "text": "I found the actual issue with the browser artifacts: the chat lane is expanding the page height instead of using an internal transcript scroller, so the summary bubbles were far below the initial viewport. I\u2019m doing a final page-scroll capture centered on the latest summary bubbles now.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 293, "prompt_index": 65, "prompt_name": "64 \u2014 Agent Summary Messages During Composition", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T08:54:57-07:00"}
