{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I\u2019ve isolated the root problem with the artifact tooling too: Puppeteer clip coordinates here are page-relative, which kept snapping back to the document top. I\u2019m switching to a plain viewport screenshot after scrolling the page to the s...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_151", "text": "I\u2019ve isolated the root problem with the artifact tooling too: Puppeteer clip coordinates here are page-relative, which kept snapping back to the document top. I\u2019m switching to a plain viewport screenshot after scrolling the page to the summary bubbles, which should give a readable final browser proof.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 296, "prompt_index": 65, "prompt_name": "64 \u2014 Agent Summary Messages During Composition", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T08:55:41-07:00"}
{"color": "cyan", "emoji": "\ud83d\udee0", "event_type": "Command Started", "message": "in progress: /bin/zsh -lc \"docker compose -f infra/compose/docker-compose.yml exec -T browser node --input-type=module - <<'EOF'\nimport puppeteer from 'puppeteer';\n\nconst sessionId = 'b3957146-e941-40d2-aa37-f611a1c8695b';\nconst screenshotPath = '/workspace/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/64_agent_summary_messages_during_composition/prompt64-summary-viewport.png';\nconst browser = await puppeteer.launch({ headless: 'new', executablePath: process.env.PUPPETEER_EXECUTABLE_PATH, args: ['--no-sandbox'] });\nconst page = await browser.newPage();\nawait page.setViewport({ width: 900, height: 1200, deviceScaleFactor: 2 });\nawait page.goto('http://frontend:8566/sessions/' + sessionId + '?stage=composition', { waitUntil: 'networkidle2', timeout: 120000 });\nawait page.waitForFunction(() => Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.workspace-chat-bubble p')).some((el) => el.textContent?.includes('Writing update')), { timeout: 120000 });\nconst scrollTop = await page.evaluate(() => {\n  const bubbles = Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.workspace-chat-bubble'))\n    .filter((el) => el.textContent?.includes('Writing update'))\n    .slice(-2);\n  if (bubbles.length === 0) {\n    return 0;\n  }\n  const top = bubbles[0].getBoundingClientRect().top + window.scrollY;\n  window.scrollTo({ top: Math.max(top - 80, 0), behavior: 'instant' });\n  return window.scrollY;\n});\nawait new Promise((resolve) => setTimeout(resolve, 500));\nconst summaryTexts = await page.evaluate(() =>\n  Array.from(document.querySelectorAll('.workspace-chat-bubble p'))\n    .map((el) => el.textContent?.trim() ?? '')\n    .filter((text) => text.includes('Writing update'))\n    .slice(-2),\n);\nawait page.screenshot({ path: screenshotPath, fullPage: false });\nconsole.log(JSON.stringify({ sessionId, screenshotPath, scrollTop, summaryTexts }, null, 2));\nawait browser.close();\nEOF\"", "raw_even