{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented checkpointed composition summaries in [composition_jobs.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/services/composition_jobs.py) and added coverage in [test_story_tools.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/tests/test_...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_164", "text": "Implemented checkpointed composition summaries in [composition_jobs.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/app/services/composition_jobs.py) and added coverage in [test_story_tools.py](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/backend/tests/test_story_tools.py). Composition now emits durable assistant chat updates at meaningful progress checkpoints, plus a segment handoff message, with content grounded in generated text and segment prompt metadata. Resume safety is handled by persisted checkpoint dedupe in job metadata, and the existing chat hydration/realtime pipeline renders the messages without a frontend code change. Code changes are committed in `1378882` (`feat(prompt-64): agent summary messages during composition`).\n\nVerification:\n- `pytest backend/tests/test_story_tools.py -q` \u2192 `26 passed`\n- `pytest backend/tests/test_session_api.py -q -k 'session_realtime_service_streams_composition_chunk_deltas or session_realtime_service_suppresses_initial_chunk_baseline_and_keeps_snapshot_recoverable or hydrate_session_endpoint_preserves_chat_navigation_bridge_history'` \u2192 `3 passed`\n- `ruff check backend/app/services/composition_jobs.py backend/tests/test_story_tools.py` \u2192 passed\n- `cd frontend && npm test -- --run src/features/session/chat/actionEchoes.test.ts src/features/session/sessionRuntimeStore.test.ts` \u2192 `11 passed`\n- `cd frontend && npm run build` \u2192 passed, with the existing Vite large-chunk warning\n- Live browser verification on the compose stack after recreating `backend`/`worker`/`frontend`; confirmed summary messages in session `b3957146-e941-40d2-aa37-f611a1c8695b`. Screenshot: [prompt64-summary-viewport.png](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/64_agent_summary_messages_during_composition/prompt64-summary-viewport.png)\n\nThe required reviewer summary was written as the final repo action at [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/64_agent_summary_messages_during_composition/summary.md). Main limitation during live QA: the local Gemini path returned 404s in this environment, so end-to-end verification relied on the app\u2019s existing fallback generation path rather than live provider responses.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 317, "prompt_index": 65, "prompt_name": "64 \u2014 Agent Summary Messages During Composition", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T09:00:27-07:00"}
